### Description

Hi there!
I've faced with strange issue.

Look, I have the app-table component which was created as a base table of the application.
Also, I have the patients-table component that inherits the app-table.

The problem is with paginator and sort, when I'm trying to refreshGrid.

There is a base component - patients. It has a two components inside it - patients-options-panel and patients-table.
I'm trying to call refreshGrid method with filters of the patients-options-panel inside patients component.

It successfully calls that method, but paginator and sort members are undefined. Why? It shoulda been initialized in the parent component - app-table. What am I doing wrong?

Also, using Chrome DevTools I see that we are in the PatientsTableComponent when I click search in options panel. And sort with paginator isn't defined here. This is really upsets me.

